FROM [Matches] AS [m]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [l].[Id], [l].[CreationTime], [l].[CreatorUserId], [l].[DeleterUserId], [l].[DeletionTime], [l].[Description], [l].[IsDeleted], [l].[LastModificationTime], [l].[LastModifierUserId], [l].[LeagueApiKey], [l].[LeagueTypeId], [l].[Name]

    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([l].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))
) AS [t] ON [m].[LeagueId] = [t].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[ClubId], [t1].[CountryId], [t1].[CreationTime], [t1].[CreatorUserId], [t1].[DeleterUserId], [t1].[DeletionTime], [t1].[Description], [t1].[IsDeleted], [t1].[LastModificationTime], [t1].[LastModifierUserId], [t1].[Name], [t1].[isNationalTeam]
    FROM [Teams] AS [t1]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_2 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([t1].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))
) AS [t0] ON [m].[HomeTeamId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[CreationTime], [c].[CreatorUserId], [c].[DeleterUserId], [c].[DeletionTime], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[LastModificationTime], [c].[LastModifierUserId], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Countries] AS [c]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_3 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([c].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))
) AS [t2] ON [t0].[CountryId] = [t2].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [t4].[Id], [t4].[ClubId], [t4].[CountryId], [t4].[CreationTime], [t4].[CreatorUserId], [t4].[DeleterUserId], [t4].[DeletionTime], [t4].[Description], [t4].[IsDeleted], [t4].[LastModificationTime], [t4].[LastModifierUserId], [t4].[Name], [t4].[isNationalTeam]
    FROM [Teams] AS [t4]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_2 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([t4].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))
) AS [t3] ON [m].[AwayTeamId] = [t3].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreationTime], [c0].[CreatorUserId], [c0].[DeleterUserId], [c0].[DeletionTime], [c0].[IsDeleted], [c0].[LastModificationTime], [c0].[LastModifierUserId], [c0].[Name]

[b].[HomeTeamScore], [b].[IsDeleted], [b].[LastModificationTime], [b].[LastModifierUserId], [b].[MatchId], [b].[PayMethodId], [b].[PaySystemId], [b].[UserId], [b].[isPaid], [t].[Id], [t].[AwayTeamId], [t].[CreationTime], [t].[CreatorUserId], [t].[DeleterUserId], [t].[DeletionTime], [t].[Description], [t].[ExpectedEndingTime], [t].[HomeTeamId], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[LastModificationTime], [t].[LastModifierUserId], [t].[LeagueId], [t].[MatchDate], [t].[MatchStatus], [t].[Name], [t].[ODD], [t].[StartingTime], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreationTime], [t0].[CreatorUserId], [t0].[DeleterUserId], [t0].[DeletionTime], [t0].[Description], [t0].[IsDeleted], [t0].[LastModificationTime], [t0].[LastModifierUserId], [t0].[LeagueApiKey], [t0].[LeagueTypeId], [t0].[Name], [t1].[Id], [t1].[ClubId], [t1].[Name], [t1].[isNationalTeam], [t3].[Id], [t3].[ClubId], [t3].[CountryId], [t3].[CreationTime], [t3].[CreatorUserId], [t3].[DeleterUserId], [t3].[DeletionTime], [t3].[Description], [t3].[IsDeleted], [t3].[LastModificationTime], [t3].[LastModifierUserId], [t3].[Name], [t3].[isNationalTeam], [t5].[Id], [t5].[AccountNumber], [t5].[CreationTime], [t5].[CreatorUserId], [t5].[DeleterUserId], [t5].[DeletionTime], [t5].[IsDeleted], [t5].[LastModificationTime], [t5].[LastModifierUserId], [t5].[SecretKey], [t5].[UserId], [t5].[isActive], [t6].[Id], [t6].[AccessFailedCount], [t6].[AuthenticationSource], [t6].[ConcurrencyStamp], [t6].[CreationTime], [t6].[CreatorUserId], [t6].[DeleterUserId], [t6].[DeletionTime], [t6].[EmailAddress], [t6].[EmailConfirmationCode], [t6].[IsActive], [t6].[IsDeleted], [t6].[IsEmailConfirmed], [t6].[IsLockoutEnabled], [t6].[IsPhoneNumberConfirmed], [t6].[IsTwoFactorEnabled], [t6].[LastModificationTime], [t6].[LastModifierUserId], [t6].[LockoutEndDateUtc], [t6].[Name], [t6].[NormalizedEmailAddress], [t6].[NormalizedUserName], [t6].[Password], [t6].[PasswordResetCode], [t6].[PhoneNumber], [t6].[SecurityStamp], [t6].[Surname], [t6].[TenantId], [t6].[UserName]
FROM [Bets] AS [b]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [m].[Id], [m].[AwayTeamId], [m].[CreationTime], [m].[CreatorUserId], [m].[DeleterUserId], [m].[DeletionTime], [m].[Description], [m].[ExpectedEndingTime], [m].[HomeTeamId], [m].[IsDeleted], [m].[LastModificationTime], [m].[LastModifierUserId], [m].[LeagueId], [m].[MatchDate], [m].[MatchStatus], [m].[Name], [m].[ODD], [m].[StartingTime]
    FROM [Matches] AS [m]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([m].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))
) AS [t] ON [b].[MatchId] = [t].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [l].[Id], [l].[CreationTime], [l].[CreatorUserId], [l].[DeleterUserId], [l].[DeletionTime], [l].[Description], [l].[IsDeleted], [l].[LastModificationTime], [l].[LastModifierUserId], [l].[LeagueApiKey], [l].[LeagueTypeId], [l].[Name]
    FROM [League] AS [l]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_2 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([l].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))
) AS [t0] ON [t].[LeagueId] = [t0].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [t2].[Id], [t2].[ClubId], [t2].[CountryId], [t2].[CreationTime], [t2].[CreatorUserId], [t2].[DeleterUserId], [t2].[DeletionTime], [t2].[Description], [t2].[IsDeleted], [t2].[LastModificationTime], [t2].[LastModifierUserId], [t2].[Name], [t2].[isNationalTeam]
    FROM [Teams] AS [t2]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_3 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([t2].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))
) AS [t1] ON [t].[HomeTeamId] = [t1].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [t4].[Id], [t4].[ClubId], [t4].[CountryId], [t4].[CreationTime], [t4].[CreatorUserId], [t4].[DeleterUserId], [t4].[DeletionTime], [t4].[Description], [t4].[IsDeleted], [t4].[LastModificationTime], [t4].[LastModifierUserId], [t4].[Name], [t4].[isNationalTeam]
    FROM [Teams] AS [t4]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_3 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([t4].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))
) AS [t3] ON [t].[AwayTeamId] = [t3].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[AccountNumber], [p].[CreationTime], [p].[CreatorUserId], [p].[DeleterUserId], [p].[DeletionTime], [p].[IsDeleted], [p].[LastModificationTime], [p].[LastModifierUserId], [p].[SecretKey], [p].[UserId], [p].[isActive]
    FROM [PayMethod] AS [p]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_4 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))
) AS [t5] ON [b].[PayMethodId] = [t5].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[AuthenticationSource], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[CreationTime], [a].[CreatorUserId], [a].[DeleterUserId], [a].[DeletionTime], [a].[EmailAddress], [a].[EmailConfirmationCode], [a].[IsActive], [a].[IsDeleted], [a].[IsEmailConfirmed], [a].[IsLockoutEnabled], [a].[IsPhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[IsTwoFactorEnabled], [a].[LastModificationTime], [a].[LastModifierUserId], [a].[LockoutEndDateUtc], [a].[Name], [a].[NormalizedEmailAddress], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[Password], [a].[PasswordResetCode], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[Surname], [a].[TenantId], [a].[UserName]
    FROM [AbpUsers] AS [a]
    WHERE ((@__ef_filter__p_5 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))) AND ((@__ef_filter__p_6 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[TenantId] = @__ef_filter__CurrentTenantId_7))
) AS [t6] ON [b].[UserId] = [t6].[Id]
WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([b].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit))
